<br>
-Who controls it?: Lets just say everyone thought the idea was good, whoever is a moderator for it could easily abuse it and put people they dont like on the list, just because they dont like them, or if someone they didnt like added someone they could ignore it.<br>
<br>
-Abuse, Example: I dont like player spinmem, so I add him to list, now this person reputation is ruined just because of something he didnt do, or a group of players does this<br>
<br>
-No Second chances: So you fuck up once.. or twice and your on it.. mistakes happen people change...<br>
